==English==
===Proper noun===
'''Ojibwe'''

# '''Ojibwe''', '''[[Ojibwa]]''', '''[[Chippewa]]''' or '''[[anishinaabemowin]]''' is a closely related group of languages and dialects of the [[w:Algonquian languages|Algonquian]] branch of the [[w:Algic languages|Algic language]] family. There are over 51,000 mother-tongue speakers in [[Canada]] and the [[United States]].

